  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The study is designed to assess the efficacy and safety of monthly injections of Omalizumab
      150 mg for 3 consecutive months, in patients with chronic idiopathic urticaria, unresponsive
      to convetional therapy by antihistamins or oral corticosteroids.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
